# AeroCraft Code Style

## File Responsibilities
- `*.types.ts` — all interfaces and type aliases only
- `*.const.ts` — all constants, numbers, strings
- `*.ts` — logic only, no inline types or magic numbers

## Naming
- No magic numbers in logic files. Extract to `numbers.const.ts`
- No magic strings. Extract to a const file
- Constant names: UPPER_SNAKE_CASE

## Imports
- Use `import type` for all type-only imports
- Path aliases: `@types/*`, `@const/*`, `@core/*`, `@postcss/*`

## Style
- No `export default` except in `src/index.ts`
- No `any` — use `unknown` when needed
- Barrel `index.ts` in every folder
- One concern per file
